{"tid":2206781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普或24至36小時內決定是否准TikTok交易","createTime":"2020-09-17T16:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T04:21:06.000Z","uid":295230,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"86af981a060672d50a94473f67b7bba87d0fd331","tid":2206781,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:51:14.000Z","msg":"美國財經頻道CNBC引述消息人士報道，總統特朗普預計在未來24至36小時內，就中國抖音海外版TikTok與甲骨文的交易，作出決定，據報甲骨文或持有TikTok在美業務兩成股份，而沃爾瑪亦有望與甲骨文合作。<br />\n<br />\n報道又說，特朗普一直與內閣成員及其他顧問會面，以決定是否批准這筆交易，但包括國務卿蓬佩奧、財長努欽及特朗普女婿庫什納在內的各人意見分歧。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普早前說，不喜歡見到TikTok的母公司中國字節跳動，保留TikTok在美業務的多數股權。白宮幕僚長梅多斯認為，如果TikTok仍然主要由中國企業營運，就達不到特朗普的目標。"},{"pid":"ca155ceb8c588bae7d8996c051c3f413a4c41921","tid":2206781,"uid":199292,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:53:02.000Z","msg":"36小時內咪36小時內<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜撚嘢叫24-36小時內"},{"pid":"ab5ff5c44bb33ea954a7389bad7debdfd7573ef8","tid":2206781,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:54:08.000Z","msg":"屌，件Mnuchin真係鬼嚟"},{"pid":"adcf38d4021318c01b0bd61452a3d57995165442","tid":2206781,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ca155ceb8c588bae7d8996c051c3f413a4c41921","tid":2206781,"uid":199292,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:53:02.000Z","msg":"36小時內咪36小時內<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜撚嘢叫24-36小時內"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:55:01.000Z","msg":"又岩喎"},{"pid":"6df78ebac0d15c14fd24d16b7dffa13d111cdf73","tid":2206781,"uid":335980,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"ca155ceb8c588bae7d8996c051c3f413a4c41921","tid":2206781,"uid":199292,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:53:02.000Z","msg":"36小時內咪36小時內<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜撚嘢叫24-36小時內"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:56:56.000Z","msg":"不少於廿四小時，又不多於36小時"},{"pid":